Ecobee,is,an,energy,solutions,provider,that,offers,WiFi,enabled,touch,screen,thermostats,and,the,corresponding,applications,to,manage,them,both,from,home,and,remotely,The,ecobee,API,provides,a,developer,interface,for,managing,ecobee,thermostats,The,API,is,capable,of,reading,updating,and,polling,thermostat,data,The,API,accepts,HTTP,GET,POST,calls,authenticates,with,OAuth,framework,and,returns,JSON,formatted,responses